node.text:
Yesterday was a big day! When I first saw this tattoo design back in 2016, I knew I wanted it. I even made my own temporary tattoo version to try it on and promised myself if I still wanted it after playing the game, I’d do it. Some of you guys may/may not remember, but last year right before the game came out, I came very, very close to losing my mom. It basically imploded my entire existence so when I finally did get to sit down and play the game after she was on the mend, this game just…fuck. It destroyed me, but it destroyed me in a wholly cathartic way - getting to see the same regrets play out on screen and knowing I had a second chance to make them right was transformative for me. So when I got the tattoo, it was a no-brainer to include my mom - that’s her handwriting at the top with the end of the Fireflies’ motto. 

The tattoo was done by my best friend from high school, @onholliday, who has become an accomplished tattooer here in Portland - it was so, so wonderful to reconnect with her through this project and I’m thrilled to have her back in my life. She did a beautiful job!!!

I know, I know, this account is for ass and titties, but sometimes I want to just stop and give you a peek into what’s happening with the person attached to the ass and titties lol 

Tattoo by @onholliday 
•••
#tattoo #lou2 #lastofus #ellie #naughtydog
